{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>在一个平面上，如果有两个点(x,y),(a,b),如果说(x,y)支配了(a,b)，这是指x≥a,y≥b;<p><p>用图形来看就是(a,b)坐落在以(x,y)为右上角的一个无限的区域内。<p><p>给定n个点的集合，一定存在若干个点，它们不会被集合中的任何一点所支配，这些点叫做极大值点。<p><p>编程找出所有的极大点，按照x坐标由小到大，输出极大点的坐标。<p><p>本题规定：n不超过100，并且不考虑点的坐标为负数的情况。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"寻找平面上的极大点 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>按x轴坐标最小到大的顺序输出所有极大点。<p><p>输出格式为:$(x\\_1,y\\_1),(x\\_2,y\\_2),...(x\\_k,y\\_k)$。<p><p>注意：输出的每个点之间有\",\"分隔,最后一个点之后没有\",\",少输出和多输出都会被判错。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>输入包括两行，第一行是正整数n，表示是点数，第二行包含n个点的坐标，坐标值都是整数，坐标范围从0到100，输入数据中不存在坐标相同的点。<p>","examples":"<input>5 \n1 2 2 2 3 1 2 3 1 4\n\n</input><output>(1,4),(2,3),(3,1)\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"提示:\n![](pic/1230.gif)\n","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1230","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}